WOWN 99.3 FM
B99.3 THE ROCK STATION
B99.3 features a mix of rock hits from the 1970s to the 2000s. It includes songs from iconic rock bands like Led Zeppelin, Rolling Stones, Pink Floyd, Motley Crue, Van Halen, Def Leppard, Foo Fighters, and Pearl Jam. This format is popular among audiences who enjoy a mix of rock music from different eras.
Example songs include "Stairway to Heaven" by Led Zeppelin, "Hotel California" by The Eagles, "Bohemian Rhapsody" by Queen, “Everlong” by Foo Fighters, “Would” by Alice in Chains, and “Better Man” by Pearl Jam.
Feature Programming: High School Sports, Local News and Sports, Weather.
Over the Air Coverage: Broad coverage over Northeast Wisconsin
